杀手队是博彩公司最看好的明年超级碗冠军球队https://www.nme.com/news/music/the-killers-are-bookies-favourites-to-headline-next-years-super-bowl-3485120?utm_source=rss&utm_medium=rss&utm_campaign=the-killers-are-博彩公司最爱的明年超级碗头条新闻Liberty DunworthFri, 18 Aug 2023 11:57:32 +0000 Music NewsNewsPopRock https://www.nme.com/?p=3485120 <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/08/the-killers-live.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="杀手们" decoding="async" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/08/the-killers-live.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/08/the-killers-live-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/08/the-killers-live-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/08/the-killers-live-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/08/the-killers-live-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/08/the-killers-live-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p>其他传闻艺术家包括泰勒·斯威夫特 (Taylor Swift)、U2 和 Imagine Dragons</p><p> <a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/the-killers-are-bookies-favourites-to-headline-next-years-super-bowl-3485120">《杀手队 (The Killers)》是博彩公司最青睐的明年超级碗头条新闻，该帖子</a>首先出现在<a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.nme.com">《NME》</a>上。</p> ; <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/08/the-killers-live.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="杀手们" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/08/the-killers-live.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/08/the-killers-live-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/08/the-killers-live-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/08/the-killers-live-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/08/the-killers-live-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/08/the-killers-live-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p><a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/the-killers">杀手队</a>被博彩公司评为明年第 58 届超级碗的热门球队。</p><ul><li><strong>阅读更多： <a href="https://www.nme.com/features/ranking-the-10-best-super-bowl-halftime-shows-in-history-3394980">历史上 10 场最佳超级碗中场表演排名</a></strong></li></ul><p><a href="https://www.mybookie.ag/sportsbook/nfl/super-bowl/halftime/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">MyBookie</a>的赔率制定者分享了这一新见解，他们推测这支美国摇滚乐队现在在标志性的超级碗中场秀下一位表演者的竞争中处于领先地位。</p><p>即将举行的第五十八届超级碗比赛将是继 1967 年亚利桑那大学交响乐团之后首次在拉斯维加斯举办的超级碗比赛。</p><p>现在，博彩公司已经确认杀手乐队看起来是最有可能在这个具有里程碑意义的时段表演的表演，并表示他们现在有 -110 的赔率登上第 58 届超级碗中场秀的舞台。</p><p>这一预测是有道理的，因为该乐队早在 2001 年就起源于拉斯维加斯，并且符合当地艺术家在拉斯维加斯首次演出的潜在愿望。</p><p>同样，该乐队自 14 年前成立以来已成为家喻户晓的名字，其热门歌曲包括《Mr.》。 《Brightside》和《Somebody Told Me》几乎肯定会受到现场观众的欢迎。 </p><figure id="attachment_3240532" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3240532" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" class="size-full wp-image-3240532" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/The-Killers-Emirates-Rob-Loud.jpg" alt="阿联酋航空的杀手" width="2000" height="1270" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/The-Killers-Emirates-Rob-Loud.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/The-Killers-Emirates-Rob-Loud-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/The-Killers-Emirates-Rob-Loud-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/The-Killers-Emirates-Rob-Loud-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/The-Killers-Emirates-Rob-Loud-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/The-Killers-Emirates-Rob-Loud-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3240532" class="wp-caption-text">杀手们。图片来源：Rob Loud/Getty</figcaption></figure><p>然而，近年来超级碗中场秀的组织者似乎不太愿意预订摇滚艺术家。</p><p>流行摇滚乐队<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/maroon-5">Maroon 5</a>参与了 2019 年的演出，酷玩乐队 ( <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/coldplay">Coldplay)</a>参加了 2016 年的演出，红辣椒<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/red-hot-chili-peppers">乐队 (Red Hot Chili Peppers) 则</a>与<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/bruno-mars">布鲁诺·马尔斯 (Bruno Mars)</a>合作，于 2014 年演出了这场大型演出。</p><p>然而，在过去的几年里，该活动转而倾向于更多的流行表演，<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/rihanna">蕾哈娜</a>被<a href="https://www.nme.com/features/the-biggest-moments-rihanna-super-bowl-halftime-show-3397259">选为最近一期在亚利桑那州州立农场体育场举行的艺术家</a>。</p><p>根据报道的-110赔率，杀手队有略高于52%的机会被选择在忠诚体育场比赛。 </p><figure id="attachment_3397773" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3397773" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" class="size-full wp-image-3397773" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/02/2023_rihanna_getty_2000x1270.jpg" alt="蕾哈娜" width="2000" height="1270" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/02/2023_rihanna_getty_2000x1270.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/02/2023_rihanna_getty_2000x1270-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/02/2023_rihanna_getty_2000x1270-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/02/2023_rihanna_getty_2000x1270-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/02/2023_rihanna_getty_2000x1270-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/02/2023_rihanna_getty_2000x1270-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3397773" class="wp-caption-text">蕾哈娜于 2023 年 2 月 12 日在亚利桑那州格伦代尔州立农场体育场举行的 Apple Music 超级碗第五十七届中场秀中表演 图片来源：Kevin Mazur/Getty Images for Roc Nation</figcaption></figure><p>紧随其后的是<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/u2">U2</a> （赔率+150）以及<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/taylor-swift">Taylor Swift</a>和<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/imagine-dragons">Imagine Dragons</a> （赔率+200）。然而，人们对斯威夫特被选中参加这项赛事的可能性表示怀疑，因为 2024 年超级碗定于 2 月 11 日举行， <a href="https://www.nme.com/en_asia/news/music/taylor-swift-eras-tour-asia-singapore-dates-tickets-3458451">与斯威夫特在日本东京的时间相同（2 月 7 日至 10 日）她全球巡演的一部分</a>。</p><p>另一位大型摇滚乐队也在最有可能在演出中表演的前 5 名艺术家之列，因为<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/foo-fighters">Foo Fighters</a>目前被列为+225 赔率。</p><p>据<a href="https://www.thesportsgeek.com/news/the-killers-favored-super-bowl-halftime-act/" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><em>《体育极客》</em></a>报道，据 NFL 内部人士透露，据传流行歌星<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/lizzo">利佐</a>也曾入围这场大型演出的候选名单，但由于<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/lizzo-sued-by-backup-dancers-for-sexual-harassment-and-creating-hostile-work-environment-3476570">对她提出性骚扰指控</a>，该名单已被官员删除。</p><p>今天（8 月 18 日）早些时候，流行巨星<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/ed-sheeran-says-he-wont-lead-a-super-bowl-halftime-performance-3484230">艾德·希兰 (Ed Sheeran) 承认，他对被选为中场秀没有兴趣</a>，并表示“这是美国的事情，我对此没有兴趣。”</p><p> <a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/the-killers-are-bookies-favourites-to-headline-next-years-super-bowl-3485120">《杀手队 (The Killers)》是博彩公司最青睐的明年超级碗头条新闻，该帖子</a>首先出现在<a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.nme.com">《NME》</a>上。</p> ;
