wake-2-delayed-to-late-october-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/alan-wake-2-delayed-to-late-october-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/alan-wake-2-delayed-to-late-october-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/brands/remedy-entertainment">Remedy Entertainment</a>和<a href="https://www.nme.com/tag/epic-games">Epic Games Publishing</a>宣布<a href="https://www.nme.com/games/alan-wake-2"><em>《心灵杀手 2》</em></a>将不再在 10 月 17 日推出，因为它试图避免发行周的拥挤。</p><ul><li><strong>阅读更多： <a href="https://www.nme.com/guides/gaming-guides/alan-wake-2-release-date-trailers-gameplay-3381506">《心灵杀手 2》的发行日期、预告片和最新消息</a></strong></li></ul><p>“十月对于游戏发布来说是一个令人惊奇的月份，我们希望这个日期的转变能够为每个人提供更多的空间来享受他们最喜欢的游戏，”该团队在 X（以前称为 Twitter）上的帖子中说道。</p><p> 10 月 16 日开始的一周内发布的其他游戏包括<em>《 <a href="https://www.nme.com/games/endless-dungeon">Endless Dungeon》</a> 、《Gangs Of Sherwood》、《Hot Wheels Unleashed 2: Turbocharged》、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/gaming-news/world-of-horror-to-leave-early-access-this-summer-3373346">《World Of Horror</a> 》、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/games/marvels-spider-man-2">《Marvel&#39;s Spider-Man 2》</a></em>和<a href="https://www.nme.com/games/super-mario-bros-wonder"><em>《Super Mario Bros. Wonder》</em></a> 。</p><blockquote class="twitter-tweet" data-width="550" data-dnt="true"><p lang="en" dir="ltr">来自《心灵杀手 2》团队的最新消息：我们将《心灵杀手 2》的发布时间从 10 月 17 日推迟到 10 月 27 日。</p><p>十月是游戏发布的绝佳月份，我们希望这个日期的转变为每个人提供更多空间来享受他们最喜欢的游戏。</p><p>我们迫不及待地想向您展示每个人的… <a href="https://t.co/GpLxyr2xvY">pic.twitter.com/GpLxyr2xvY</a></p><p> ——心灵杀手 2 (@alanwake) <a href="https://twitter.com/alanwake/status/1692174551466316121?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw">2023 年 8 月 17 日</a></p></blockquote><p><script async src="https://platform.twitter.com/widgets.js" charset="utf-8"></script></p><p>续作目前计划于 10 月 27 日在<a href="https://www.nme.com/tag/pc">PC</a> 、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/tag/ps5">PlayStation 5</a>和<a href="https://www.nme.com/tag/xbox-series-xs">Xbox Series X|S</a>上上市。距离最初的 PC 和<a href="https://www.nme.com/tags/xbox-360">Xbox 360</a>游戏问世已有十多年了，Remedy Entertainment 表示，这是迄今为止“最雄心勃勃、最复杂、最重要”的游戏。</p><p> “ <em>《心灵杀手 2》</em>有五个概念，”扮演回归主角的演员伊尔卡·维利 (Ilkka Villi) 在最新一期<em>EDGE</em>杂志（来自<em><a href="https://www.theloadout.com/alan-wake-2/interview-scope-important" target="_blank" rel="noopener">The Loadout</a></em> ）的采访中透露。</p><p>萨加·安德森是游戏的<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/gaming-news/alan-wake-2-reveals-october-launch-and-two-protagonists-with-an-unsettling-trailer-3448031">第二个可玩主角</a>，她偶然发现了一个关于自己的恐怖故事，而这个故事突然开始变成现实。当艾伦和萨加试图逃离越来越近的力量时，两条“独立的黑暗和令人不安的道路”将开始在游戏过程中交织在一起。</p><p>与原版游戏不同， <em>《心灵杀手 2》</em>将采用不同的对话选项，因为 Remedy Entertainment 的灵感来自于<a href="https://www.nme.com/games/control"><em>《控制》</em></a>的<a href="https://www.videogameschronicle.com/features/alan-wake-2-interview-true-detective-was-definitely-on-our-mind/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">叙事发展</a>。</p><p> <em>《失忆症》</em>系列开发商<a href="https://www.nme.com/brands/frictional-games">Frictional Games</a>近日表示， <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/gaming-news/frictional-games-to-take-time-off-from-making-horror-games-3471605">未来不会再开发新的恐怖游戏</a>。 “我认为，沉浸感、个人旅程和整体视野是摩擦游戏的定义特征，而不仅仅是恐怖游戏，”创意总监 Thomas Grip 解释道。</p><p> <a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.nme.com/news/gaming-news/alan-wake-2-delayed-to-avoid-clashing-with-other-games-3485022">为了避免与其他游戏发生冲突，《心灵杀手 2》的</a>帖子首先出现在<a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ;
科里·泰勒透露了他最被高估和低估的活结歌曲https://www.nme.com/news/music/corey-taylor-reveals-his-most-over-and-under-erated-slipknot-songs-3485074?utm_source=rss&utm_medium=rss&utm_campaign=corey-taylor-reveals-他最被高估和低估的活结歌曲Liberty DunworthFri, 18 Aug 2023 10:06:02 +0000 Music NewsNewsMetal https://www.nme.com/?p=3485074 <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/06/Corey-Taylor@2000x1270.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="活结" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/06/Corey-Taylor@2000x1270.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/06/Corey-Taylor@2000x1270-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/06/Corey-Taylor@2000x1270-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/06/Corey-Taylor@2000x1270-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/06/Corey-Taylor@2000x1270-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/06/Corey-Taylor@2000x1270-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p>他承认他仍然唱着最被高估的歌曲来让粉丝开心，尽管这是“我他妈的屁股上的痛苦”</p><p> <a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/corey-taylor-reveals-his-most-over-and-under-rated-slipknot-songs-3485074">科里·泰勒 (Corey Taylor) 透露他最被高估和低估的 Slipknot 歌曲的帖子</a>首先出现在<a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ; <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/06/Corey-Taylor@2000x1270.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="活结" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/06/Corey-Taylor@2000x1270.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/06/Corey-Taylor@2000x1270-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/06/Corey-Taylor@2000x1270-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/06/Corey-Taylor@2000x1270-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/06/Corey-Taylor@2000x1270-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/06/Corey-Taylor@2000x1270-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p><a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/corey-taylor">科里·泰勒</a>在一次新的采访中透露了他个人认为最被高估和最低估的<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/slipknot">活结</a>歌曲。</p><ul><li><strong>阅读更多： <a href="https://www.nme.com/features/music-interviews/corey-taylor-interview-cmf2-ptsd-slipknot-look-outside-your-window-3480518">科里·泰勒：“不要觉得自己很特别——我讨厌所有人！”</a></strong></li></ul><p>这次讨论是在<a href="https://www.revolvermag.com/music/corey-taylor-picks-slipknots-most-overrated-and-underrated-songs#overrated-wait-and-bleed" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><em>Revolver</em></a>的一次新采访中进行的，其中<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/stone-sour">Stone Sour</a>和 Slipknot 的主唱透露了他对后者广泛的唱片的个人看法。</p><p>自 1997 年加入乐队以来，乐队现已拥有七张录音室专辑，泰勒承认，也许并不奇怪，有些曲目他不一定喜欢表演。</p><p>在采访中，他回忆道，他发现他们唱片中最被高估的歌曲是热门歌曲《Wait And Bleed》——这是他们 1999 年同名专辑中众多歌迷最喜欢的歌曲之一。</p><p> “我非常公开地说‘等待和流血’让我他妈的很痛苦，”他开始说道。 “我已经唱这首歌 26 年了，伙计们，这首歌从未变得如此容易！</p><p> “但我仍然和活结乐队以及我的个人项目一起唱这首歌，这告诉你我是多么的神经病，因为我知道人们喜欢这首歌，”他补充道。 “所以，你必须这么做——听着，这是一个很好的问题。” </p><figure id="attachment_3461734" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3461734" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" class="size-full wp-image-3461734" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/06/Slipknot-posing.jpg" alt="活结。图片来源：安东尼·斯坎加" width="2000" height="1270" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/06/Slipknot-posing.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/06/Slipknot-posing-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/06/Slipknot-posing-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/06/Slipknot-posing-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/06/Slipknot-posing-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/06/Slipknot-posing-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3461734" class="wp-caption-text">活结。图片来源：安东尼·斯坎加</figcaption></figure><p>另一方面，他也承认他从他们2004年的专辑《Vol.》中找到了一首歌。 3: (The Subliminal Verses)&#39;，成为他们唱片中最不受重视的曲目。</p><p> “对我来说，活结乐队最被低估的歌曲是《Danger — Keep Away》，”他承认。 “我喜欢这两个版本，专辑中的版本和最终发行的未剪辑版本。那首歌有一些美丽的部分，”他证实道。</p><p>据<a href="https://loudwire.com/corey-taylor-slipknot-songs-most-overrated-underrated/" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><em>Loudwire</em></a>报道，《Wait And Bleed》是 Slipknot 有史以来播放次数第四多的歌曲，自 24 年前发行以来，已出现在他们的 964 首歌曲列表中。然而，“危险 – 远离”显然从未在他们无数的现场表演中播放过。</p><p>目前，Slipknot 计划的唯一即将举行的演出是九月的蓝岭摇滚音乐节，因此粉丝们可能不应该对“Danger – Keep Away”首演抱有太高的希望。</p><p>另一方面，科里·泰勒 (Corey Taylor) 将于下个月发行他的第二张个人专辑《CMFT2》，这是他 2020 年首张专辑《CMFT》的后续作品。为了庆祝即将发布的专辑（9 月 1 日），泰勒将<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/corey-taylor-announces-cmft2-uk-and-european-tour-preorder-listen-new-single-3467850">开始他自己的头条巡演</a>。 </p><figure id="attachment_3467858" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3467858" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" class="size-full wp-image-3467858" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/Corey-Taylor@2000x1270.jpg" alt="科里·泰勒 2023" width="2000" height="1270" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/Corey-Taylor@2000x1270.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/Corey-Taylor@2000x1270-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/Corey-Taylor@2000x1270-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/Corey-Taylor@2000x1270-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/Corey-Taylor@2000x1270-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/Corey-Taylor@2000x1270-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3467858" class="wp-caption-text">科里·泰勒 2023。图片来源：Marina Hunter/出版社</figcaption></figure><p>这次长途跋涉将于下周（8 月 25 日）在科罗拉多州丹佛市举行一场演出开始，并于 11 月跨越大西洋进行<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/corey-taylor-announces-cmft2-uk-and-european-tour-preorder-listen-new-single-3467850">一系列英国和欧洲巡演</a>。</p><p>第一场演出将在利兹 O2 学院举行，随后将在伍尔弗汉普顿举行。从那里开始，他将在曼彻斯特、格拉斯哥和伦敦等城市停留，然后在本月晚些时候前往法国、德国和荷兰。 <a href="https://ticketmaster-uk.tm7559.net/c/2862475/431519/7559?sharedid=NME&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ticketmaster.co.uk%2Fcorey-taylor-tickets%2Fartist%2F1608825" target="_blank" rel="noopener">在这里</a>找到剩余的门票。</p><p>泰勒上周在接受<em>NME</em>采访时<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/corey-taylor-on-tackling-ptsd-on-cmft2-a-bridge-between-people-dealing-with-it-3483639">回忆了 PTSD 主题如何在即将发行的专辑中发挥的作用</a>，特别是在歌曲“Post Traumatic Blues”中。</p><p>他还<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/corey-taylor-teases-release-of-slipknots-lost-album-look-outside-your-window-3482056">调侃了活结乐队遗失的专辑《Look Outside Your Window》的发行</a>——这张专辑是他本人、Sid Wilson、Jim Root 和 Shawn &#39;Clown&#39; Crahan 在 2008 年录制的《All Hope Is Gone》的同时录制的。 </p><p><iframe loading="lazy" title="Corey Taylor 谈论“CMF2”、PTSD 意识以及 Slipknot 的下一步发展" width="696" height="392" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/jhKn5spvKbQ?feature=oembed" frameborder="0" allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share" allowfullscreen></iframe></p><p> Clown 此前<a href="https://www.nme.com/features/music-interviews/slipknot-clown-new-guy-tortilla-man-knotfest-we-are-not-your-kind-knotfest-cruise-look-outside-your-window-2601547">在 2020 年接受 NME 采访时</a>透露，乐队几乎在 2019 年圣诞节期间放弃了它，但最终决定不这样做，因为他们不希望它干扰他们的第六张录音室专辑《 <a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/slipknot-we-are-not-your-kind-review-2534063">We Are Not Your Kind</a> 》。此外，今年一月，Crahan 表示<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/lost-slipknot-album-look-outside-your-window-could-be-released-this-year-says-clown-3373724">今年终于可以见到曙光</a>。</p><p>现在，在<em>NME</em>的新采访中，泰勒提供了进一步的更新，并表示专辑尚未发行部分是他的错。</p><p> “你提出这个问题实际上很有趣。 I was talking to Clown about it the other day and he goes, &#39;One of the reasons it hasn&#39;t come out is because you keep putting shit out which keeps conflicting with when I want to release it!&#39; I was like, &#39;Fuck dude, why didn&#39;t you tell me?&#39;” he said.</p><p> “It&#39;s sounding like he&#39;s got a release date that he can finally lock in and I have promised him that I won&#39;t release anything that will ruin that. I think it&#39;s going to be next year – finally, man!”</p><p> The post <a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/corey-taylor-reveals-his-most-over-and-under-rated-slipknot-songs-3485074">Corey Taylor reveals his most over and under-rated Slipknot songs</a> appeared first on <a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a> .</p> ;
